snippet.title: Combined_Arms Dev diary 3-4-20: Tech Monk
snippet.description:
https://www.patreon.com/CombineKegan?fan_landing=true



Just a brief video covering what I've been doing the past few months, the Tech Monk is pretty much done at this point and I've been working on other features of this big update. If you're interested in keeping closer tabs on what I've been working on, I now have a discord server for my work and stuff:


https://discord.gg/wyNKfh4

More progress stuff to follow!
